@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'eInvoice Serial Number Status'
define view entity ZETR_DDL_I_DELIVERY_NUMSTAT
  as select from zetr_t_edocnum as Numbers
  association        to parent zetr_ddl_i_delivery_serials as _deliverySerials     on  $projection.CompanyCode  = _deliverySerials.CompanyCode
                                                                                   and $projection.SerialPrefix = _deliverySerials.SerialPrefix
  association [1..1] to zetr_ddl_i_delivery_parameters     as _eDeliveryParameters on  $projection.CompanyCode = _eDeliveryParameters.CompanyCode
{
  key Numbers.bukrs as CompanyCode,
  key Numbers.nrobj as NumberRangeObject,
  key Numbers.serpr as SerialPrefix,
  key Numbers.numrn as NumberRangeNumber,
  key Numbers.gjahr as FiscalYear,
      Numbers.numst as NumberStatus,
      _eDeliveryParameters,
      _deliverySerials
}
where
  Numbers.nrobj = 'ZETR_EDL'
